## 7. Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

**Q. Are there any fees for using the application?**  
A. Basic Bible reading and search functionalities are provided completely free of charge. Certain premium features can also be accessed at no cost by using Talents acquired through in-app activities.

**Q. Can I read the Bible without an internet connection?**  
A. Yes, Bible translations downloaded to your device in advance can be read in an offline environment. However, specific features such as cloud synchronization require a network connection.

**Q. How is my personal information protected?**  
A. We collect only the absolute minimum amount of information required and manage your data securely via Google Firebase\'s verified security infrastructure. For more detailed information, please refer to our Privacy Policy below.

**Q. Which Bible translations are available?**  
A. Currently, we offer KRV, Revised Version, Common Translation, KJV, ASV, WEB, CUV, and more. We plan to continuously expand our library subject to copyright negotiations.

